Camera controls: (keyboard)
  F - third person follow
  H - for helicopter view
  T - for top view
  P - to lock on tower view

Camera controls: (mouse)
  In helicopter view:
    Press the middle mouse button to look around

Cube controls:
  Arrow keys for respective movement

Level Change:
  Press "1" for level 1
  Press "2" for level 2

  NOTE : use makefile_linux for compiling on linux (original is for mac)

  NOTE: Please have a compiled assimp folder inside the current with name "assimp", or compile assimp and copy the lib files to the lib folder in current project
